short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically changes the favicon of Google docs to first emoji in the doc title.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tired of a sea of blue and green rectangles in your chrome tabs? Spice things up by putting emojis in your document titles and have that become the tab icon.

Code available: https://github.com/pcarleton/favmoji
